title: Speaker NA issues production order of four MNAs
content:
ISLAMABAD, Jan 03 (APP):Speaker National Assembly Asad Qaiser had issued production orders of members Shahid Khaqan Abbasi, Syed Khurshid Shah, Ahsan Iqbal and Saad Rafiq.
The orders had been issued under rule 108 of Rules of Procedure and Conduct of Business of National Assembly.
The National Assembly Secretariat had sent copies of production orders to the relevant departments.
